Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.67,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{If only I didn't have this cold...}Giá mà em không bị cảm thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:16.21,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-Foundation!
