Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.32,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Well then...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.86,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ph-Ph-Phalanx!
