Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.38,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Their weakness is Earth viruses.}Điểm yếu của bọn chúng là virút Trái Đất.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:07.88,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}S-S-Super! F-F-Fire! W-W-Work Type!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.58,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Nyarlko is incredible...}Nyaruko ghê thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.88,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Listen to Nyarlko's sneezes.}Nghe tiếng hắt xì của Nyaruko kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:11.88,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,V-V-VF-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.55,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't be afraid, you fools!}Bọn ngốc các ngươi đừng có xoắn lên chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:19.37,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{You have already been vaccinated!}Các ngươi đã được tiêm vắc xin rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:19.85,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.09,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(\fs70)}{What?!}Cái gì?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.25,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{It wasn't foreshadowing after all?}Vậy đó không phải là điều các ngươi che dấu sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:30.99,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{After our last retreat, we prepared against all possible threats!}Sau lần rút quân lần trước, chúng ta đã lường trước hết mọi khả năng rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.59,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Big West!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:34.36,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Nyarlko!}Nyaruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.91,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{She's burning up!}Cô nóng quá!
